{"tid":1980718,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際線] twitter 是否應該大舉攻擊譚德塞殘害奧羅莫人嘅黑歷史","createTime":"2020-04-20T09:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T13:59:37.000Z","uid":31215,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6dcb9b9a0cd8f523574ace128108cd2ebe9a3d","tid":1980718,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"等D左膠支持佢支持得咁開心?<br />\n殺人兇手，恐怖份子就有佢份<br />\n<br />\n由於提格利尼亞人（Tigrayans）只佔埃國人口的極少數（約 6%），所以提人陣 (佢個恐怖組織)也奉行恐怖統治，濫捕殘殺異見者，強佔國內最大族群奧羅莫人（約 34%）的土地。在 2005 年，「人權觀察」的報告狠批提人陣在掌權期間，犯下多種人權罪行；1990 年代，美國一度把左傾的提人陣視作恐怖組織，到今天依然名列馬利蘭大學「全球恐怖主義資料庫」（Global Terrorism Database）。經過連年內亂，直到 2018 年，埃塞俄比亞人民革命民主陣線才進行改組，不再由提人陣掌控。奧羅莫民主黨（Oromo Democratic Party）阿比艾哈邁德（Abiy Ahmed）接任總理，立即進行大刀闊斧的政治改革，釋放數以萬計的政治犯，更在 2019 年獲得諾貝爾和平獎。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞就在提格雷地區長大，1991 年門格斯圖倒台不久，他就遠赴倫敦衛生與熱帶醫學院讀免疫學碩士，2000 年在諾定咸大學完成社區衛生博士學位。由於他學歷高，而且具提格雷成長背景，2001 年立刻就成為提格雷區衛生局局長，2005 年更一躍成為衛生部長，那年譚德塞才剛滿 40 歲，<span style=\"color: red;\">他還是該國第一位沒有臨床醫學背景的衛生部長。譚德塞競選世衛總幹事時就被踢爆在 2006、2009 和 2011 年，三度隱瞞在奧羅莫地區的霍亂災情，致使數以百計患者失救死亡。</span>他到 2012 年更進一步，出任外交部長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/04/15/road-to-head-of-who-tedros-adhano/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2F2020%2F04%2F15%2Froad-to-head-of-who-tedros-adhano%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=98072221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/04/15/road-to-head-of-who-tedros-adhano/</a><br />\n<br />\n更詳細可聽沈旭暉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SMoZKDre9W8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSMoZKDre9W8&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=cd7baad9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SMoZKDre9W8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://theredelephants.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Screen-Shot-2020-04-10-at-5.36.45-PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftheredelephants.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FScreen-Shot-2020-04-10-at-5.36.45-PM.png&h=e4b22358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有綁架異見人士嫌疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTedros Adhanom played a key role in kidnapping of prominent dissident<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ThQk9Hb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FThQk9Hb.jpg&h=88a05159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ecadforum.com/2017/05/05/tedros-adhanom-played-a-key-role-in-kidnapping-of-prominent-dissident/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fecadforum.com%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2Ftedros-adhanom-played-a-key-role-in-kidnapping-of-prominent-dissident%2F&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=d87e9dc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://ecadforum.com/2017/05/05/tedros-adhanom-played-a-key-role-in-kidnapping-of-prominent-dissident/</a><br />\n<br />\n4年前已經有聯署反對佢做WHO director<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/we-oppose-tedros-adhanom-s-candidacy-for-director-general-of-who\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fwe-oppose-tedros-adhanom-s-candidacy-for-director-general-of-who&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPvFBXrQbHxe6tNmRytRnjp4%3D&h=3466840c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/we-oppose-tedros-adhanom-s-candidacy-for-director-general-of-who</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">D左膠仲有咩講?</span></span>"},{"pid":"4e6da06bad30c432cd2bbd192969dea716e0411b","tid":1980718,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a6fb0f5f25b98341b10f922cba9d57e896ba2eac","tid":1980718,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"同支共一樣，都係恐怖組織"},{"pid":"1861ea2fb312fb1b0863490ea79023f5e7b9e958","tid":1980718,"uid":108756,"